# Fast DeepSeek Coder - Optimized for Autocomplete Speed
FROM deepseek-coder:6.7b

# System prompt for autocomplete
SYSTEM You are a code completion assistant. Complete code accurately and quickly.

# Speed-first parameters for autocomplete
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192               # Smaller context for speed
PARAMETER num_predict 256            # Short completions
PARAMETER temperature 0.1            # Very deterministic
PARAMETER top_p 0.95                 # High probability mass
PARAMETER top_k 50                   # Slightly larger top-k
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.05        # Light repetition penalty
PARAMETER num_thread 16              # All threads
PARAMETER num_gpu 1                  # GPU acceleration

# Fast stop sequences
PARAMETER stop "\n\n"
PARAMETER stop "```"
